hat Gautam has been pressurizing PM Oli to nominate him to the Upper House.\n\nIn today\u2019s meeting with Dahal, PM Oli also expressed the dilemma whether or not take Gautam to the National Assembly as he believes that Dr Khatiwada is the right person to lead the Ministry of Finance at this crucial time.\n\nIt may be noted that the meeting of the party\u2019s Secretariat on February 26 had decided to take Gautam to the NA.\n\nWhile PM Oli wants to nominate Dr Khatiwada to the NA and continue him as finance minister, Gautam has insisted that he should be taken to the Upper House.\n\nSources said that Gautam has been demanding that he be taken to the NA and be appointed to the post of Deputy Prime Minister and Finance Minister, which PM Oli is \u201cnot very interested\u201d.\n\nPrime Minister Oli is learned to have asked leader Gautam to vacate the Dolpa constituency and contest for the House of Representatives.","title":"Dahal-Oli meet: PM Oli in dilemma on nominating Gautam to NA - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/02/124597/","video":[]}
